298
00:18:44,240 --> 00:18:44,760
Yes.

299
00:18:45,920 --> 00:18:46,480
Mr. Xu.

300
00:18:46,760 --> 00:18:47,920
It’s been a day.

301
00:18:48,040 --> 00:18:49,440
