317
00:19:32,320 --> 00:19:33,840
when Mo Lin told me.

318
00:19:36,200 --> 00:19:38,080
I was late.

319
00:19:40,360 --> 00:19:42,800
Or I’ll make you lose even worse.

320
00:19:43,440 --> 00:19:44,520
I don't understand

321
00:19:44,680 --> 00:19:46,720
why you should take the blame for Qin Qi.

322
00:19:47,440 --> 00:19:48,680
He showed no mercy

323
00:19:48,800 --> 00:19:49,800
to you before.

324
00:19:49,960 --> 00:19:52,080
I just don't like Shanhai Gang.

325
00:19:53,480 --> 00:19:55,240
