356
00:21:40,720 --> 00:21:42,680
I am not alone, either.

357
00:21:46,840 --> 00:21:47,680
I promise you,

358
00:21:49,920 --> 00:21:52,400
if you dare do Su Tang the slightest harm,

359
00:21:54,400 --> 00:21:56,600
you will die.

360
00:21:58,480 --> 00:21:59,360
And

361
00:22:00,080 --> 00:22:01,680
if you fail this mission,

362
00:22:03,640 --> 00:22:06,240
do you think Shanhai Gang will let you go easily?

363
00:22:08,720 --> 00:22:10,200
Senior Xu, you will know

364
00:22:11,400 --> 00:22:13,280
how I practice

365
00:22:14,240 --> 00:22:15,800
this ability of being beaten.

366
00:22:17,880 --> 00:22:19,600
Dealing with demon,

367
00:22:22,320 --> 00:22:24,240
aren’t you afraid?

368
00:22:33,000 --> 00:22:34,480
Those two who were sent to track

369
00:22:34,520 --> 00:22:35,320
Xu Weifeng have no further information.

370
00:22:35,760 --> 00:22:37,240
They might have been killed.

371
00:22:39,040 --> 00:22:41,000
There is something wrong with Xu Weifeng.

372
00:22:41,240 --> 00:22:42,360
Now that we have found out,

373
00:22:42,760 --> 00:22:44,360
