380
00:22:55,720 --> 00:22:57,800
But Xu Weifeng is the son of Xu Yanling.

381
00:22:58,360 --> 00:22:59,440
Words alone are no proof.

382
00:22:59,800 --> 00:23:00,680
If we open mouth rashly,

383
00:23:00,880 --> 00:23:02,600
