386
00:23:07,240 --> 00:23:08,000
General Qin.

387
00:23:09,840 --> 00:23:10,560
General Qin.

388
00:23:10,920 --> 00:23:11,600
Bad news.

389
00:23:11,960 --> 00:23:12,600
Now

390
00:23:12,760 --> 00:23:13,920
the army knew

391
00:23:14,080 --> 00:23:15,080
Xu Tianbing was dead.

392
00:23:15,320 --> 00:23:16,840
