404
00:23:36,360 --> 00:23:37,040
Minister Xia.

405
00:23:37,920 --> 00:23:39,200
I have my own opinion on this.

406
00:23:39,840 --> 00:23:41,240
The conflict may break out at any moment.

407
00:23:41,360 --> 00:23:42,760
What’s the point of your opinion?

408
00:23:43,080 --> 00:23:45,040
Do you want to wait until the mutiny

409
00:23:45,280 --> 00:23:47,240
