457
00:26:30,160 --> 00:26:31,600
Big Dipper please go and help.

458
00:26:32,280 --> 00:26:33,200
Miss Qin.

459
00:26:34,520 --> 00:26:36,320
Lu Ping isn’t the disciple of Big Dipper anymore.

460
00:26:36,680 --> 00:26:39,720
Why should Big Dipper help?

461
00:26:41,200 --> 00:26:42,040
Master Li.

462
00:26:42,520 --> 00:26:44,000
I’m willing to make amends for

463
00:26:44,240 --> 00:26:45,720
Lu Ping’s previous trespass.

464
00:26:46,480 --> 00:26:48,760
But Lu Ping was also jailed for
the civilians of two countries.

465
00:26:49,320 --> 00:26:51,000
Will Big Dipper be afraid of power

466
00:26:51,400 --> 00:26:52,440
